thread.title: BRIEF-Jiangsu Jiejie Microelectronics sees FY 2017 net profit to up 15 pct to 30 pct

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Jiangsu Jiejie Microelectronics sees FY 2017 net profit to up 15 pct to 30 pct

organizations.name: reuters) - jiangsu jiejie microelectronics co ltd

text:
Jan 25 (Reuters) - Jiangsu Jiejie Microelectronics Co Ltd :
* Sees FY 2017 net profit to increase by 15 percent to 30 percent, or to be 133.9 million yuan to 151.4 million yuan
* Says FY 2016 net profit was 116.4 million yuan
* Says steady growth of main business as main reason for the forecast
Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/HfSyJt
